{"synckey":1781604782,"updated":[{"bookId":"41147996","bookmarkId":"41147996_8_2167-2213","chapterUid":102,"markText":"微习惯策略会让你在感觉良好的状态下做出改变，而成效最佳的改变恰恰源于感觉良好，而非感觉糟糕。","range":"1896-1942","createTime":1634707046,"type":1},{"bookId":"41147996","bookmarkId":"41147996_8_1654-1958","chapterUid":102,"markText":"要想设计出成功的习惯并改变自身行为，你需要做到3件事：·　停止自我批评；·　把你的愿望拆解成微行为；·　将每一次错误当成是一种新发现，并利用它们不断改进。","range":"1534-1704","createTime":1634690493,"type":1},{"bookId":"41147996","bookmarkId":"41147996_8_1399-1490","chapterUid":102,"markText":"如果你掌握了正确的方法，那么养成好的习惯、做出积极的改变可以很容易。除了正确的方法，你还需要一个基于人类心理学运作方式的系统，一个让改变更容易的流程，一个不依赖猜测或错误原则的工具。","range":"1292-1383","createTime":1634605052,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"前言","chapterUid":102,"chapterIdx":8}],"book":{"bookId":"41147996","version":1755586843,"format":"epub","soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/39/YueWen_41147996/s_YueWen_41147996.jpg","title":"福格行为模型","author":"B.J.福格","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KCRfzm$.t8?Q%5s;~9M|ad","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#002032"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#00223d"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#002449"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#033547"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#003752"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#00395f"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#1a4d60"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#004f6b"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#005178"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#005590"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#106883"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#006d9c"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#396677"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#0087b5"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#548090"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#0085a9"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#6f9aa9"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#539db6"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#23a0c3"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#00a5dd"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#49bbdd"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#00beeb"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#00c1fa"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#a0cfde"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#85d3ec"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#00ddff"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#d2e6ed"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#00fbff"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#23a0c3"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#49bbdd"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#E5F2F3"